NK015(ba)015:0: rak+ta ba sa d+aa ng+ka ra s+ya sh+r+ai r+sha ma //
NK015(ba)015:2: / khrag 'thung dam pa rgyan gyi dabu'o //
NK015(ba)015:3: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK015(ba)015:4: bsgyur ba khrag 'thung gi dkyil 'khor la /
NK015(ba)015:5: ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa la bzhi ste /
NK015(ba)015:6: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK015(ba)015:7: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK015(ba)015:9: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin no //
NK015(ba)015:11: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK015(ba)015:13: skye ba med la thams cad skyes //
NK015(ba)015:14: skyes pa nyid na'ang skye ba med //
NK015(ba)015:16: skye ba med pa ni chos kyi dbyings /
NK015(ba)015:17: skyes pa ni 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad de /
NK015(ba)015:18: skyes pa'i dus de nyid na chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin du shes pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:19: chos thams cad ye nas gnas pa'i gnas lugs yin pas /
NK015(ba)015:20: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin ces bya'o //
NK015(ba)015:21: kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK015(ba)015:23: stong pa nyid du rab gsal bas //
NK015(ba)015:24: snying rje'i yul ni bsgom par bya //
NK015(ba)015:26: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad snying rje'i yul yin te /
NK015(ba)015:27: don dam par chos kyi dbyings stong pa nyid du rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal kyang /
NK015(ba)015:29: sdug bsngal gyi rten du gyur pa'i phyir /
NK015(ba)015:30: rtogs pa dang ldan pa'i snying rje'i yul yin te /
NK015(ba)015:31: snying rje'i yul sems can snang ba ni /
NK015(ba)015:32: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin ces bya'o //
NK015(ba)015:35: h'u nges pa la ni rdo rje che //
NK015(ba)015:36: de la dpal chen he ru ka /
NK015(ba)015:39: sku gsung thugs tshang bar yod de /
NK015(ba)015:40: thugs kyi rang bzhin yi ge h'u mthing nag las /
NK015(ba)015:41: rdo rje nag po rtse dgu pa /
NK015(ba)015:42: khro zhal bcu drug dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)015:44: de las dpal kun bzang he ru ka mthing nag dbu dang phyag zhabs ni nges pa med pas /
NK015(ba)015:46: re zhig slob dpon pad+ma'i dgongs pas 'di ltar bzhed do //
NK015(ba)015:48: zhabs rnam pa brgyad dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)015:49: dbus kyi zal gsum mthing nag /
NK015(ba)015:52: phyag dang po gnyis kyi rdo rje dang thod khrag /
NK015(ba)015:53: de'i 'og ma gnyis g.yon na ro /
NK015(ba)015:54: g.yas kyis de'i glo snying 'byin cing gsol ba /
NK015(ba)015:55: de'i 'og ma gnyis g.yas nyi ma /
NK015(ba)015:56: g.yon zla ba thugs ka na bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)015:57: de'i 'og ma gnyis g.yas na khyung /
NK015(ba)015:59: dam nyams pa'i rnal 'byor pa la 'gyed pa /
NK015(ba)015:60: de'i 'og ma gnyis g.yas na rlung /
NK015(ba)015:61: g.yon na me'i 'khor lo thogs te /
NK015(ba)015:62: 'jig rten thams cad 'thor zhing bsreg par byed pa /
NK015(ba)015:63: de'i 'og ma gnyis g.yas na chu'i dkyil 'khor /
NK015(ba)015:64: g.yon na ri rab thogs te /
NK015(ba)015:66: nga rgyal thams cad gnon par byed pa /
NK015(ba)015:69: g.yon na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che snod dang bcas pa bsnams pas /
NK015(ba)015:70: rnal 'byor pa la cis kyang mi tshugs shing /
NK015(ba)015:71: dngos grub rnam gsum ster bar mdzad pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:72: zhabs brgyad ni lha chen po brgyad la bardzisa pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:73: sku la dpal chas bcu drug gis brgyan cing /
NK015(ba)015:74: bskal pa'i me ri 'bar ba'i dbus na /
NK015(ba)015:75: sku 'bar ba'i gar dgu dang ldan te /
NK015(ba)015:76: 'jigs pa'i dus kyi me bzhin du bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:77: de ni dkyil 'khor thams cad bskyed pa'i bdag po yang yin /
NK015(ba)015:79: rgyu yi thing nge 'dzin ces bya'o //
NK015(ba)015:80: yongs su rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin la don gsum gyis bstan te /
NK015(ba)015:81: khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK015(ba)015:82: khro bo gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK015(ba)015:83: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK015(ba)015:84: de la dang po khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis te /
NK015(ba)015:85: bdag gi sras su rgyal ba bskyed pa'i sgo nas bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK015(ba)015:86: rgyal ba'i sras su bdag bskyed pa'i sgo nas dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK015(ba)015:87: de la bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul la gnyis kyi dang po rten bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:89: b+h+r+aum dur khrod chen po rab 'jigs pa'i //
NK015(ba)015:90: khrag gi rgya mtsho 'khrugs pa'i dkyil //
NK015(ba)015:91: ces pa la sogs pa 'phros te /
NK015(ba)015:92: rang gi thugs ka nas e yam bam mam kem ram rnams spros pa las /
NK015(ba)015:93: e las chos 'byung gru gsum mthing nag rgya khyon
NK015(ba)015:94: nam mkha' dang mnyam pa de'i steng du yam las
NK015(ba)015:95: rlung gi dkyil 'khor sra zhing mkhregs pa /
NK015(ba)015:96: kha dog dud kha dbyibs zla gam du gyur par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:97: de'i steng du bam las khrag gi rgya mtsho rba rlabs 'khrugs pa /
NK015(ba)015:99: de'i steng du mam las sha chen gyi sa gzhi sra zhing 'jam la /
NK015(ba)015:101: de'i steng du kim las keng rus kyi ri rab nag po /
NK015(ba)015:102: kha khyer dang rgya mnyam pa /
NK015(ba)015:103: rak+ta khrag ki zham chu zu lu lu 'bab par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:104: de'i steng du ram las bskal pa'i me ri 'bar bar gyur te /
NK015(ba)015:105: me de'i phyed mar chad pas 'og gi 'byung ba rnams cha snyom pa /
NK015(ba)015:106: phyed ri rab de'i kha rgyan du gyur te /
NK015(ba)015:107: bskal pa'i me ri 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du gyur par sgom mo /
NK015(ba)015:110: phyogs bcu'i zhing khams thams cad khyab nas /
NK015(ba)015:111: de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su dgongs /
NK015(ba)015:112: byang chub sems dpa'i spun du dgongs /
NK015(ba)015:113: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro rnams kyi rje bor dgongs /
NK015(ba)015:114: de nas phyogs bcu'i gzhal yas khang gi che yon thams cad gnang ba'i tshul du bsdus te /
NK015(ba)015:117: gzhal yas khang bskyed par gsal gdab bo //
NK015(ba)015:118: rang gi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum smug nag gcig 'phros pa las /
NK015(ba)015:121: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK015(ba)015:122: phyi rdo rje'i gur khang dang bcas pa /
NK015(ba)015:123: dbu rtse bar 'khyams gnyis rim du gnas pa /
NK015(ba)015:124: phyi thod pa skam po las byas pa /
NK015(ba)015:125: bar thod par ri thod rnyid /
NK015(ba)015:126: nang thod pa rlon pa las byas pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:127: zur bzhir gnam lcags kyi 'dzer chen bzhi gdab pa /
NK015(ba)015:128: 'dzer mgor nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bzhi shar ba phyogs bzhir 'khor lo dang /
NK015(ba)015:132: steng rdo rje nag po'i bla gab tu chud pa /
NK015(ba)015:133: bya skyib lnga dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)015:134: rgyal chen bzhi la sgo skyes byas pa /
NK015(ba)015:135: lha chen po brgyad kyis nang gi ka ba byas pa /
NK015(ba)015:136: klu chen po brgyad kyis steng gi gdung ma bres pa /
NK015(ba)015:137: gza' chen po brgyad kyis kha bad lding ba /
NK015(ba)015:138: rgyu skar nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi phyam gyis mdzes pa /
NK015(ba)015:139: 'brug gi ri dwags kyi rkan sgra sgrogs pa /
NK015(ba)015:140: gnam lcags kyi thog ser 'bab pa /
NK015(ba)015:142: ba dan rtse gsum pas brgyan pa skal pa'i rlung nag 'tshub pa /
NK015(ba)015:143: ye shes kyi me ri 'bar ba /
NK015(ba)015:147: sbrul nag gi za ra tshag gis brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)015:148: nyi zla'i skar khung lding ba /
NK015(ba)015:150: kun tu yang nang du gyur par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:152: dbus su gru gsum mthing nag zla gam dmar po gsum dad ldan pa /
NK015(ba)015:153: de'i phyi rol 'khor lo sngon po rtsibs bzhi la me 'bar ba /
NK015(ba)015:154: rtsibs mchan nag po rdo rje'i brag gis gtam pa /
NK015(ba)015:155: phyi rol rdo rje mu khyud kyis bskor ba /
NK015(ba)015:156: gru chad bzhi glo 'bur bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)015:157: de'i phyi rol lha snam nang ma sgo khyud bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)015:158: bar 'khyams phyi nang gis brgyan pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:159: de nas gtan bting ba ni /
NK015(ba)015:160: dbus kyi gru gsum ru tra pho mo dang /
NK015(ba)015:162: de'i steng du seng ge brgyad kyi khri byung /
NK015(ba)015:163: shar phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du /
NK015(ba)015:164: dri za dang tshangs pa pho mo'i steng du /
NK015(ba)015:165: ma he dmar skya brgyad kyi khri byung ngo //
NK015(ba)015:166: lho phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du /
NK015(ba)015:167: grul bum dang gshin rje pho mo'i steng du /
NK015(ba)015:168: gzig brgyad kyi khri byung ngo //
NK015(ba)015:169: nub phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du /
NK015(ba)015:171: klu'i steng du stag brgyad kyi khri byung ngo //
NK015(ba)015:172: byang phyogs 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du /
NK015(ba)015:173: gnod sbyin pho mo dang de'i steng du /
NK015(ba)015:174: dam brgyad kyi khri byung ngo //
NK015(ba)015:175: de dag gi bar du rin po che'i khri'i steng du mu tig gi d+r+wa ba dang /
NK015(ba)015:178: nyi ma'i gdan re re bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:179: rtsibs chen bzhi gru chad bzhi dang brgyad la /
NK015(ba)015:180: zhing bsnol ma brgyad kyi steng du nyi ma'i gdan re re /
NK015(ba)015:181: lha snam la zhing rkyang pa brgyad kyi steng du nyi ma /
NK015(ba)015:182: sgo bzhir zhing rkyang pa bzhi'i steng du nyi ma /
NK015(ba)015:184: nang zhing tshal pa shar du drug /
NK015(ba)015:187: byang du drug ste nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi steng du nyi ma'i tshal pa re re bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:188: de nas brtan pa lha'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK015(ba)015:189: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK015(ba)015:190: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK015(ba)015:191: khro rgyal ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK015(ba)015:192: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings las ni //
NK015(ba)015:193: khro mo dbang phyug mngon phyungs te //
NK015(ba)015:195: bdag gi thugs ka nas yum khro mo dbang phyug ma /
NK015(ba)015:196: sku mdog mthing nag yab dang 'dra ba'am /
NK015(ba)015:197: yang na zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK015(ba)015:199: g.yon pas thod khrag bsnams pa phyungs la /
NK015(ba)015:200: yab yum ma chags thabs kyi rol pa mdzad pa las /
NK015(ba)015:201: h'u h'u h'u b+hi shwa badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha dz+wa la man+dala phata phata phata /
NK015(ba)015:202: ha la ha la ha la h'u /
NK015(ba)015:204: bdag nyid dbu dang phyag zhabs stong khams kyi rdul snyed dang mnyam pa zhes 'byung ste /
NK015(ba)015:209: phyag na stong khams kyi rdul snyed kyi mtshon cha 'dzin par gyur te /
NK015(ba)015:211: khro bo zhal phyag nges pa med pa /
NK015(ba)015:212: sku tshad stong gsum tsam las /
NK015(ba)015:213: grangs stong khams kyi rdul phra rab snyed thon te /
NK015(ba)015:214: stong khams kyi drag byed thams cad ni bsgral /
NK015(ba)015:215: sems can thams cad kyi don byas nas /
NK015(ba)015:216: slar phyogs bcu nas tshur 'dus pa las /
NK015(ba)015:217: 'bras bu'i khrag 'thung du bzhengs pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:218: bdag nyid dbus su b+hud+d+ha khrag 'thung sku mdog smug nag /
NK015(ba)015:221: phyag g.yas kyi dang po na 'khor yug /
NK015(ba)015:224: g.yon dang po na b+han d+ha khrag gis bkang ba /
NK015(ba)015:227: phyag mtshan de dag la me 'bar ba /
NK015(ba)015:228: yum b+hud+d+ha kro ti shwa ri ma /
NK015(ba)015:234: shar phyogs kyi khro bo rnams gcig tu 'dus pa las /
NK015(ba)015:235: badz+ra khrag 'thung sku mdog mthing nag /
NK015(ba)015:239: phyag drug gi g.yas dang po na rdo rje /
NK015(ba)015:243: lho phyogs kyi khro bo rnams gcig tu 'dus pa las /
NK015(ba)015:244: rat+na khrag 'thung sku mdog ser nag /
NK015(ba)015:248: yag g.yas dang po na ral gri /
NK015(ba)015:251: g.yon dang po na b+han d+ha khrag gis bkang ba /
NK015(ba)015:255: nub phyogs kyi khro bo rnams gcig tu 'dus pa las /
NK015(ba)015:256: pad+ma khrag 'thung sku mdog dmar nag /
NK015(ba)015:260: phyag g.yas dang pa na dgra s+t+wa /
NK015(ba)015:263: g.yon dang po na b+han d+ha /
NK015(ba)015:266: byang phyogs kyi khro bo rnams gcig tu 'dus pa las /
NK015(ba)015:267: karma khrag 'thung sku mdog ljang nag /
NK015(ba)015:271: phyag g.yas dang po na gsol /
NK015(ba)015:274: g.yon dang po na b+han d+ha /
NK015(ba)015:277: yum rnams ni sku mdog yab dang mthun pa zhal gcig phyag gnyis /
NK015(ba)015:279: g.yon b+han d+ha dmar chen gyis bkang ba yab la stobs pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:280: yab yum kun la chas chen po bcu drug dang ldan pa /
NK015(ba)015:281: zhal gdang zhing spyan bsgrad pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:282: so so'i gdan la zhabs brkyang bskum gyi tshul gyis bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)015:283: sku la bskal pa'i me ri 'bar ba /
NK015(ba)015:284: ral pa khams na gyen du 'khyil ba las /
NK015(ba)015:285: thod pa skam pa'i phreng bas bcing ba /
NK015(ba)015:286: 'bar ba'i gar dgu dang ldan pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:287: gnas kyi lha mo brgyad bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:290: ma mo chen mo brgyad du gyur te /
NK015(ba)015:295: g.yon na b+han+d+ha dmar chen gyis bkang ba gsol ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:296: bam bsnol ma'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:297: lhor rkun mo sku mdog ser mo /
NK015(ba)015:298: phyag gnyis kyis mda' gzhu 'gengs te /
NK015(ba)015:299: gtso bo'i thugs kar gzir ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:300: nub tu rmongs byed ma sku mdog dmar nag /
NK015(ba)015:301: g.yas na chu srin gyis rgyal mtshan phyar ba /
NK015(ba)015:302: g.yon b+han d+ha dmar chen gyis bkang ba gsol ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:303: byang phyogs su brlag byed ma sku mdog mthing nag /
NK015(ba)015:305: g.yon zhing chung ngu'i mgo nas gsol ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:307: spos mo sku mdog dmar ser /
NK015(ba)015:308: phyag g.yon pas zhing bzung nas /
NK015(ba)015:309: g.yas kyis de'i rgyu ma zhags par 'dren pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:310: lho nub tu gtum mo sku mdog ljang ku /
NK015(ba)015:311: g.yon thod khrag g.yas rdo rjes dkrugs shing gsol ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:312: nub byang du sme sha can /
NK015(ba)015:313: sku mdog nag mo phyag gnyis kyis zhing bzung nas khong pa nas glo snying 'dren cing za ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:314: byang shar mtshams su ma tshogs ma sku mdog mthing skya /
NK015(ba)015:315: phyag gnyis kyis zhing gi mgo lus phral ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:318: stag gi sham thabs mnga' ba /
NK015(ba)015:319: rgyu ma'i phreng bas sku la dkris pa /
NK015(ba)015:323: dbu dang sku la thod pa'i phreng bas brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)015:324: klu chen po brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)015:325: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i dbus na /
NK015(ba)015:327: dbyings las byung ba'i ngo mtshar dang /
NK015(ba)015:328: dpal chen thugs las sprul pa'i ngo mtshar dang /
NK015(ba)015:329: gdul bya 'dul ba'i ngo mtshar gsum dang bcas nas bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:330: yul gyi lha mo brgyad bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:331: byang chub sems kyi sprin la he /
NK015(ba)015:333: mgo brnyan ma brgyad du gyur te /
NK015(ba)015:334: shar phyogs su seng ha ma sku mdog ser mo /
NK015(ba)015:335: seng ge'i mgo can kha na ro za ba /
NK015(ba)015:336: phyag gnyis rtse gsum gyi phyag rgya bsnol nas /
NK015(ba)015:337: zhabs gnyis 'gying thabs kyis zhing rkyang pa'i gdan la bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:338: lho phyogs su byakri mu ka smu mdog dmar nag /
NK015(ba)015:340: mdun du zhing la 'bru tshags su blta ba /
NK015(ba)015:341: phyag gnyis kyis rtse gcig gi phyag rgya bsnol ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:342: nub phyogs su sri la mu kha nag mo /
NK015(ba)015:344: phyag gnyis kyis zhing gi lpags pa thogs nas chu ser ldag pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:345: byang phyogs su shwa na mu ka sku mdog sngon mo //
NK015(ba)015:347: phyag gnyis kyis zhing bzung nas /
NK015(ba)015:348: khong pa bkral te nang gi glo snying la blta ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:349: shar lhor kri ta mu ka sku mdog dmar nag /
NK015(ba)015:351: phyag g.yas gri khug g.yon thod khrag bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:352: lho nub mtshams su kam ka mu ka sku mdog snar mo /
NK015(ba)015:354: phyag gnyis kyis zhing phrag pa la khur ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:355: nub byang mtshams su kha kha mu kha bya rog gi mgo can /
NK015(ba)015:358: g.yon na b+han+d+ha rgyu mas bkang ba gsol ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:360: byang shar mtshams su hu lu mu ka 'ug pa'i mgo can /
NK015(ba)015:362: g.yas lcags kyu g.yon b+han+d+ha khrag gis bkang ba gsol ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:363: phra men ma de brgyad kyi rgyan dang cha lugs ni /
NK015(ba)015:364: gnas kyi lha mo brgyad dang 'dra ba las /
NK015(ba)015:365: khyad par du sku la gshog pa skyes pa /
NK015(ba)015:366: 'khor yang phra men ma de 'dra ba'i tshogs kyis bskor ba /
NK015(ba)015:367: zhing rkyang pa'i gdan la bzhugs pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:368: byang chub sems kyi sprin las phata /
NK015(ba)015:370: dkyil 'khor gyi sgo bzhir sgo ma bzhi bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:371: shar sgor rta gdong lcags kyu ma /
NK015(ba)015:372: sku mdog dkar po'am sngon mo /
NK015(ba)015:375: g.yon b+han d+ha dmar chen gyis bkang ba'i nang na /
NK015(ba)015:376: rta mgo ljang ku phyung ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:377: lho sgor phag gdong zhags pa ma sku mdog ser nag /
NK015(ba)015:378: phyag gnyis kyis rgyu ma'i zhags pa bsnams pa'i rtse mo na phag rgod kyi mche bas mtshan pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:379: nub sgor nyi zla lcags sgrog ma sku mdog dmar mo /
NK015(ba)015:380: phyag gnyis lcags sgrog bsnams te /
NK015(ba)015:381: mdo mig smin mtshams na yod de /
NK015(ba)015:382: nyi zla'i ga bu'i nang na rnal 'byor pa'i tshe 'dzin pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:385: byang sgor dril bu ma sku mdog ljang nag /
NK015(ba)015:386: phyag g.yas na dril bu bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)015:387: g.yon na b+han+d+ha bdud rtsi lngas bkang ba'i nang nas /
NK015(ba)015:388: sangs rgyas snang ba mtha' yas kyi sku lte ba yan chad phyungs ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:389: lha mo 'di bzhi ni dpal chas bcu drug dang ldan te /
NK015(ba)015:390: yum kro ti shwa ri ma dang 'dra'o //
NK015(ba)015:391: kun kyang zhing rkyang pa'i gdan la bzhugs te /
NK015(ba)015:392: ngo mtshar gsum dang bcas nas rngam pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:394: dgyes pa'i sprin las phyogs bcu nas /
NK015(ba)015:396: thams cad sngar bas kyang khros te /
NK015(ba)015:397: dmag chas pa la rem rem byas pa dang 'dra bar /
NK015(ba)015:398: shin tu yang khros par gyur to //
NK015(ba)015:399: de dag ni khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul te /
NK015(ba)015:400: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pa'i rtags so //
NK015(ba)015:401: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis kyis bstan pa'i 'go ma /
NK015(ba)015:402: rgyal ba'i sras su bdag bskyed pa'i sgo nas /
NK015(ba)015:405: rang gi ngang tshul de bzung nas //
NK015(ba)015:406: bskul tshig 'di yang rab tu brjod /
NK015(ba)015:408: gtso bo'i sku la gnyis su gyur te /
NK015(ba)015:409: shar phyogs kyi sgor gshegs nas /
NK015(ba)015:411: sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni /
NK015(ba)015:412: zhes pa la sogs pas bskul bas /
NK015(ba)015:413: gtso bo'i thugs ka nas 'od bskal ba'i me dpung lta bu byung bas /
NK015(ba)015:414: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum gyi bag chags thams cad bsreg nas /
NK015(ba)015:415: sems rnam par dag pa gser zhun ma lta bur gyur pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:417: rang gi sems yi ge h'u mthing nag tu gyur te /
NK015(ba)015:418: gtso bo'i thugs kar thim pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:420: yab yum gnyis ma chags thabs kyi rol pa mdzad pa sku'i dbyibs su brgyud /
NK015(ba)015:421: gsang ba rdo rje'i lam du byung /
NK015(ba)015:422: yum gyi pad ma'i mkha' la bab pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:424: byang chub sems kyi 'od dpung dkar dmar 'dres pa las /
NK015(ba)015:425: gtso bo yab yum yang 'od du zhu nas /
NK015(ba)015:426: byang chub sems kyi 'od dpung la thim /
NK015(ba)015:427: rigs bzhi khrag 'thung rnams kyang h'u zhes brjod cing 'od dpung la thim /
NK015(ba)015:430: sgo ma bzhis phata ces brjod cing /
NK015(ba)015:431: thams cad dbus kyi gdan thog tu 'od dpung du gyur pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:432: bde ba chen po'i dbang ngo /
NK015(ba)015:434: / 'od de yang mi dmigs pa stong pa nyid du gnas pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:435: ye shes rang gnas kyi dbang ngo //
NK015(ba)015:436: dbang de rnams bskur ba'i dgos pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:437: ye nas sangs rgyas pa yin kyang /
NK015(ba)015:439: rig pa lhun gyi grub par bya ba dang /
NK015(ba)015:440: rgyal ba'i sras su bdag bskyed pa'i phyir ro //
NK015(ba)015:441: yongs su rdzogs pa'i cho 'phrul gyi gnyis pa gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor la lnga ste /
NK015(ba)015:442: cho ga gsum gyis gtso bo yab yum bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK015(ba)015:444: byin gyis rlabs pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK015(ba)015:445: yum gyi mkha' gsang las dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul dang /
NK015(ba)015:446: gsang ba'i byang chub sems kyis mchod pa 'bul ba'i cho 'phrul lo //
NK015(ba)015:447: gtso bo yab yum bskyed pa'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK015(ba)015:448: dbus kyi gdan thog tu h'u mthing nag sgril mar gnas pa las /
NK015(ba)015:449: h'u mthing nag grangs med pa 'phros pas /
NK015(ba)015:450: drag dal ni 'khu 'phang 'dril ba tsam sgra ni bong grags pa tsam mo //
NK015(ba)015:452: sems can gyi ngag gi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)015:453: bde gshegs gsung gi rgyud bskul /
NK015(ba)015:454: slar tshur 'dus pa las bzhi bo'i h'u la thim pas /
NK015(ba)015:455: rdo rje dang b+han+d+hara drag dal ni ser ba 'bab pa tsam /
NK015(ba)015:456: sgra ni seng ge'i nga ro tsam /
NK015(ba)015:459: de la phyag mtshan grangs med pa 'phros pas sems can gyi yid kyi sgrib pa sbyang ba /
NK015(ba)015:460: bder gshegs thugs kyi rgyud bskul /
NK015(ba)015:462: las yab yum gnyis kyi sku phra mor gyur /
NK015(ba)015:463: de la sku phra mo grangs med pa 'phros drag dal ni thog 'bab pa tsam /
NK015(ba)015:464: sgra ni 'brug sgra ldir ba tsam mo //
NK015(ba)015:467: sems can gyi lus kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK015(ba)015:468: bder gshegs sku'i rgyud bskul nas /
NK015(ba)015:469: he ru ka'i skur gyur te /
NK015(ba)015:470: sku de rnams slar 'dus dbus kyi sku la thim pa las /
NK015(ba)015:471: dpal khrag 'thung chen po'i skur gyur te /
NK015(ba)015:478: dbu ral pa khams nag srid pa'i rtse mor 'khyil ba /
NK015(ba)015:479: ral pa'i rtsa bar sbrul dang thod pas bcing ba /
NK015(ba)015:480: phyag drug gi g.yas dang po na rdo rje nag po rtse dgu pa /
NK015(ba)015:481: g.yon dang po dung chen khrag gis bkang ba dkrug cing gsol ba /
NK015(ba)015:482: g.yas bar ma na stong gi 'jig rten 'khor yug /
NK015(ba)015:484: g.yon bar ma na dgra sta /
NK015(ba)015:486: sku la dpal chas bcu drug gis brgyan pa /
NK015(ba)015:487: zhabs bzhi brkyang bskum gyi tshul du bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)015:488: bskal pa'i me ri 'bar ba'i klong na 'bar ba'i gar dgu dang ldan te /
NK015(ba)015:489: dgyes shing ngo mtshar ba'i tshul gyis bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:490: yum badz+ra kro ti shwa ri ma /
NK015(ba)015:493: g.yon pas dung chen khrag gis bkang ba yab la stobs pa /
NK015(ba)015:494: chas chen po bcu drug gis brgyan pa la /
NK015(ba)015:495: za byed gzig gi sham thabs can /
NK015(ba)015:496: sku mdog mthing nag 'jol sgeg gi tshul du yab la 'khril te bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:497: yab kyi thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' rang 'dra
NK015(ba)015:498: ba gcig nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la bzhugs par bsgom
NK015(ba)015:499: / de'i thugs kar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK015(ba)015:500: rdo rje nag po rtse dgu pa /
NK015(ba)015:501: de'i lte bar nyi ma la h'u mthing nag gi tha mar /
NK015(ba)015:502: ru lu 'bru brgyad kha dog mthing nag gis g.yas su 'khor ro //
NK015(ba)015:504: de'i nang du nyi ma'i steng du /
NK015(ba)015:505: h'u mthing nag la ru lus g.yon phyogs su 'khor ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:506: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi gnyis pa dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK015(ba)015:508: rtags kyi dbang gnyis su shes par bya ste /
NK015(ba)015:510: ma h+aa sh+au nya ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)015:511: zhes brjod pas sku de yang brdal ba chen po chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos par bsgom /
NK015(ba)015:513: spyi bor mi bskyod pa sku mdog mthing ka /
NK015(ba)015:515: ma h+aa a dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)015:516: zhes pas yab yum gyi sku de yang chos kyi
NK015(ba)015:517: sku mi 'gag pa tsam yin par shes par bya'o
NK015(ba)015:519: dpral ba'i phyogs su rnam par snang mdzad sku mdog dkar po /
NK015(ba)015:521: ma h+aa pra t+ya bek+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)015:522: zhes pas lha'i sku de dag kyang gdul bya'i bsam
NK015(ba)015:523: pa mtha' yas pa bsam gyis mi khyab par bsam
NK015(ba)015:525: ltag par snang ba mtha' yas sku mdog dmar po /
NK015(ba)015:527: ma h+aa sa man+ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)015:529: de ltar rgyal ba'i sku ma 'gag pa dang /
NK015(ba)015:530: dbyings ma skyes pa gnyis dbyer med par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:532: rna ltag g.yas su rin chen 'byung ldan sku mdog ser mo /
NK015(ba)015:534: ma h+aa kri t+y+aa nush+th+aa n+ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)015:536: rgyal ba'i sku ma 'gag pa ni gzhan don do //
NK015(ba)015:537: ngo bo ma skyes pa ni bdag don te /
NK015(ba)015:538: don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:540: rna ltag g.yon pa'i steng du don yod grub pa sku mdog ljang ku /
NK015(ba)015:542: byin gyis rlabs pa'i cho 'bul ni /
NK015(ba)015:543: sarba ta th+aa ga ra ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)015:545: bdag gi spyi bo'i nang du sku rdo rje sku mdog dkar po /
NK015(ba)015:548: zla ba'i gdan la bzhugs pa /
NK015(ba)015:550: de'i thugs kar 'khor lo gyis mtshan par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:551: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aak+ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)015:553: lce pad+ma 'dab brgyad kyi steng du /
NK015(ba)015:554: gsung rdo rje sku mdog dmar po g.yas pad+ma /
NK015(ba)015:556: de'i thugs kar pad+ma gyis mtshan par /
NK015(ba)015:558: sarba ta th+aa ga ta tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)015:560: thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du /
NK015(ba)015:561: thugs rdo rje sku mdog sngon po /
NK015(ba)015:562: g.yas rdo rje g.yon dril bu bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)015:563: de'i thugs kar rdo rje h'u gis mtshan par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:564: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa a nu rwa
NK015(ba)015:565: ga na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a
NK015(ba)015:567: lte bar rin chen zur brgyad kyi steng du /
NK015(ba)015:568: chags pa'i rdo rje sku mdog ser po /
NK015(ba)015:569: g.yas na rin chen zur brgyad pa /
NK015(ba)015:570: g.yon na dril bu bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:571: de'i thugs kar rin po che zur brgyad pas mtshan pa bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:572: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK015(ba)015:574: gsang gnas chos 'byung gru gsum gyi steng du /
NK015(ba)015:575: mchod pa'i rdo rje sku mdog ljang gu /
NK015(ba)015:577: g.yon na dril bu bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)015:578: de'i thugs kar ral gri ham gis mtshan par bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:579: mkha' gsang byin gyis rlabs shing dkyil 'khor spro ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK015(ba)015:580: yab kyi gsang ba'i gnas su h'u las /
NK015(ba)015:585: yum gyi gsang ba'i gnas su /
NK015(ba)015:586: pam las pad+ma dmar po 'dab ma brgyad pa'i steng du /
NK015(ba)015:588: de gnyis kyi bar du ma las nyi ma'i dkyil
NK015(ba)015:589: 'khor gyis ye shes kyi drod bskyed par bsgom mo
NK015(ba)015:594: de yang phyogs bcu'i b+hud+d+ha thams cad rang gi zhal du zhugs /
NK015(ba)015:601: a nu r+aa ga ya ham /
NK015(ba)015:603: a nu r+aa ga ya mi /
NK015(ba)015:605: gsang ba rdo rje'i lam nas /
NK015(ba)015:606: yum gyi pad+ma'i mkha' la b+h+r+aum dmar po gcig 'phros pa las dkyil 'khor du gyur te /
NK015(ba)015:608: sgo gdan khri dang bcas pa /
NK015(ba)015:611: byang chub sems kyi cha gnyis pa la /
NK015(ba)015:617: so so'i gdan thog tu bab pa las /
NK015(ba)015:619: de rnams las h'u bcu la rigs lnga yab yum bcur gyur /
NK015(ba)015:620: ha las nang gi lha mo brgyad /
NK015(ba)015:621: he las phyi'i lha mo brgyad /
NK015(ba)015:624: sku mdog phyag mtshan dang cha lugs //
NK015(ba)015:626: khro bo rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor ltar bsgom zhing /
NK015(ba)015:628: h'u nges pa la ni rdo rje che //
NK015(ba)015:629: de la dpal chen he ru ka /
NK015(ba)015:632: / 'jigs pa yi ni dus ltar drag /
NK015(ba)015:633: sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni /
NK015(ba)015:636: mchog nyid bsgrub par 'gyur pas na //
NK015(ba)015:637: phyag rgya chen por bdag sbyor cig /
NK015(ba)015:638: badz+ra ar+ya te dza ting dzah badz+ra a mu kha h'u /
NK015(ba)015:640: badz+ra b+hasmi ba la ba tu ho /
NK015(ba)015:641: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru
NK015(ba)015:642: ka ma h+aa tsan+ta sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na da
NK015(ba)015:643: ha pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK015(ba)015:644: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai sarba dush+tana h'u phata /
NK015(ba)015:645: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+ta
NK015(ba)015:646: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u
NK015(ba)015:647: h'u h'u phata / ma h+aa badz+ra d+h+aa ra ma
NK015(ba)015:648: h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai dz+wa li n+ai h'u phata
NK015(ba)015:649: h'u h'u phata / / rat+na ma h+aa sh+r+ai he
NK015(ba)015:650: ru ka ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dush+tan+ta ka ha na
NK015(ba)015:651: da ha pa tsa h'u h'u h'u phata /
NK015(ba)015:652: ma h+aa s+aur+ya rat+na ma h+aa kro d+hi shwa r+ai bi da ma h'u phata /
NK015(ba)015:653: pad+ma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+ta
NK015(ba)015:654: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u
NK015(ba)015:655: h'u h'u phata / h+r+aihsh+ru ta sa man+ta pad+ma ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai kh+aa hi h'u phata /
NK015(ba)015:656: karma ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa tsan+ta
NK015(ba)015:657: sarba dush+t+aan+ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u
NK015(ba)015:658: h'u h'u phata / sarba a mo g+ha ma h+aa kro d+he shwa ri bi shwa h'u phata /
NK015(ba)015:659: che mchog mnyam nyid 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas /
NK015(ba)015:660: gdug pa 'dul mdzad thugs rje khros pa'i rgyal //
NK015(ba)015:661: gsang sngags rmad 'byung drag po'i phrin las kyis //
NK015(ba)015:662: lhun gyis grub par byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK015(ba)015:664: he ru ka lnga la nyi ma zla ba pad+ma'i steng du /
NK015(ba)015:666: de'i thugs kar phyag mtshan dang po rnams la ru lus bskor ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:667: kha dog ni sku mdog bzhin no //
NK015(ba)015:668: yum lnga la nyi ma'i steng du /
NK015(ba)015:669: b+han+d+ha'i nang du nyi ma'i steng du /
NK015(ba)015:670: h'u las ru lus g.yon phyogs su 'khor ro //
NK015(ba)015:671: ma mo nyi shu'i thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du rdo rje rtse lnga pa'i lte ba la /
NK015(ba)015:674: phra men ma brgyad la he /
NK015(ba)015:676: de'i tha mar ru lu'am rang sngags kyis g.yas bskor du 'khor ro //
NK015(ba)015:677: dbang mo la nyi ma'i steng du /
NK015(ba)015:678: b+han+d+ha phyed po la b+h+yos mtshan pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:679: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi mchod pa 'bul ba'i cho 'phrul ni /
NK015(ba)015:681: khams drug gi lha mor gyur te /
NK015(ba)015:682: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams la rgyas par mchod de /
NK015(ba)015:683: de nas rang bzhin lhun gyi grub pa'i dkyil 'khor du 'don pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:684: badz+ra khrag 'thung yab yum gyi sngags 'don pas /
NK015(ba)015:686: yum rang gi yum la bstim mo //
NK015(ba)015:687: de bzhin du b+hud+d+ha khrag 'thung yab yum spyan drang la dkyil 'khor gyi shar du bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:688: rat+na khrag 'thung yab yum spyan drangs la lhor bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:689: pad+ma khrag 'thung yab yum spyan drang la nub tu bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:690: karma khrag 'thung yab yum spyan drang la byang du bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:691: gnas kyi lha mo brgyad spyan drang la so so'i gdan la bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:692: phra men ma brgyad spyan drangs la lha snam la bzhugs /
NK015(ba)015:693: sgo ma bzhi spyan drang la sgo bzhir bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:694: de dag kyang so so'i sngags kyis yum gyi mkha' nas spyan drang la /
NK015(ba)015:695: rang rang gi sngags kyis gdan la cag ge bzhugs so //
NK015(ba)015:696: der yang lha thams cad gsal gdab /
NK015(ba)015:697: phyag rgya spros pa ltar na /
NK015(ba)015:699: byin gyis brlabs pa'i lha lnga dang /
NK015(ba)015:700: thugs ye shes sems dpa' gsum brtsegs kun la tshang bar bya'o //
NK015(ba)015:701: de dag ni rang bzhin lhun gyi grub pa'i dkyil
NK015(ba)015:702: 'khor khrag 'thung sum cu 'don pa'i cho 'phrul lo
NK015(ba)015:703: // rang bzhin lhun gyi grub pa'i cho 'phrul gyi gnyis pa /
NK015(ba)015:704: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:705: bar 'khyams kyi zhing tshal pa nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyi steng du /
NK015(ba)015:706: b+h+yo nyi shu rtsa brgyad las /
NK015(ba)015:707: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad du bskyed pa
NK015(ba)015:708: ni rang rang gi sngags kyis lhag lhag bskyed de
NK015(ba)015:709: / shar gyi b+h+yo drug las ma drug bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:712: rdo rje srin mo kha dog smug nag g.yas na b+han+d+ha rlon pa bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:716: tshangs pa dmar ser dbu bzhi sbrul gyi cod pan can /
NK015(ba)015:721: lha chen mo sku mdog dkar ljang /
NK015(ba)015:725: gtog 'dod ma sngon mo g.yas 'khor lo /
NK015(ba)015:728: gzhon nu ma sku mdog dmar mo g.yas na mdung bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:732: brgya byin dkar mo g.yas rdo rje gding po bsnams pa /
NK015(ba)015:733: de drug ni ma ltar byams pa'i ma drug ces bya'o //
NK015(ba)015:738: ma mo drug bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:742: rdo rje dmar mo sku mdog dmar mo /
NK015(ba)015:747: bdud rtsi dmar mo g.yas na pad+ma bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:751: zhi ba mo dkar mo g.yas na me tog pun+da ri ka bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:755: be con ma ljang nag g.yas thod dbyug 'phyar ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:758: srin mo dmar ser g.yas thod khrag 'thung ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:761: za ba mo ljang nag g.yas rgyu zhags bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:762: de drug ni snying rje sring ltar brtse ba'i ma drug ces bya ste /
NK015(ba)015:763: rnal 'byor pa la sring mo'i tshul 'dzin cing /
NK015(ba)015:766: nub phyogs kyi b+h+yo drug las /
NK015(ba)015:767: ma mo drug bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:771: dga' ba mo dmar mo phyag g.yas na gter bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:773: re ti re ma ti b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)015:775: khrag gi myos ma sku mdog dkar mo /
NK015(ba)015:778: e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)015:780: gcig pur spyod ma sku mdog ser mo /
NK015(ba)015:781: g.yas na spu gri bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:783: ma nu ha ra ma b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)015:785: 'dod pa mo dmar mo phyag g.yas na mda' gzhu bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:790: phyag g.yas na nor gyi bum pa bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:794: rlung lha mo sku mdog sngo skya g.yas na ba dan lce brgyad bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:796: dga' ba mdza' ltar yid 'ong gi ma drug ces bya ste /
NK015(ba)015:797: rnal 'byor pa'i nye gnas bzhi la /
NK015(ba)015:798: mdza' mo'am gzungs ma'i cha 'dzin pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:801: byang gi b+h+yo drug las ma drug bskyed pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:803: ma h+aa m+aa r+aa na b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)015:805: gsod byed ma kha dog nag mo g.yas ral gri bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:809: mi mo sku mdog dmar mo /
NK015(ba)015:810: g.yas na me sgron bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:814: phag mo kha dog nag mo /
NK015(ba)015:815: g.yas na phag rgod kyi mche ba'i zhags pa bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:819: rgan byed ma sku mdog nag mo /
NK015(ba)015:820: g.yas na zhing chung za ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:824: sna chen mo sku mdog dkar ljang g.yas na thod pa bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:828: chu lha mo sku mdog sngon mo g.yas na sbrul zhags bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:829: de drug ni btang snyoms bka' nyan gyi ma drug ces bya ste /
NK015(ba)015:830: nye gnas bzhi la bran mo'i cha 'dzin /
NK015(ba)015:832: tshad med pa btang snyoms la dbang byed do //
NK015(ba)015:834: badz+ra ma h+aa k+aa l+aa b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)015:836: rdo rje nag mo sku mdog nag mo g.yas lcags kyu'o //
NK015(ba)015:840: shan pa mo sku mdog dmar ser /
NK015(ba)015:841: g.yas na zhags pa bsnams so //
NK015(ba)015:843: badz+ra bum pa ka ra na b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)015:845: rdo rje bum rna mo sku mdog mdar nag /
NK015(ba)015:846: g.yas na lcags sgrog bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:848: badz+ra lam+bo d+ha ra na b+h+yo /
NK015(ba)015:852: ma mo 'di bzhi'i mtshan nyid ni gong ma'i phyogs su bartsi'o /
NK015(ba)015:854: / 'di rnams kyi phyag g.yon na b+han+d+ha dmar chen gyis bkang ba'i nang nas /
NK015(ba)015:855: rdo rje rtse gsum pas mtshan pa bsnams pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:856: kun kyang zhing lpags kyi sked chings dang /
NK015(ba)015:857: stag lpags kyi sham thabs dang /
NK015(ba)015:858: thod pa rlon pa'i 'phreng ba dang /
NK015(ba)015:859: dar dang me tog gi cod pan dang /
NK015(ba)015:860: rin po che sna tshogs kyi rgyan du byas pa /
NK015(ba)015:862: zhing tshal pa'i gdan la brkyang bskum gyis bzhugs pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:863: de rnams kyi thugs ka na thod pa tshal pa b+h+yos mtshan pa re re yod de /
NK015(ba)015:864: dbu la rdo rje lnga pa re res mtshan pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:865: so so'i 'khor 'bum phrag dang bcas pa bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:866: de ltar dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo 'dir bskyed pa 'dis /
NK015(ba)015:867: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu'i chos kyi dbyings kyis gar khyab par /
NK015(ba)015:868: dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsam gyis mi khyab par 'byung bar bsgom mo //
NK015(ba)015:869: de dag ni rang bzhin lhun gyi grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK015(ba)015:870: de yan chad ting nge 'dzin bzhi'i sgo nas sems rang snang gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa'o //
NK015(ba)015:871: de nas ye shes rang snang gi dkyil 'khor gyis byin gyis brlabs pa la yang don bcu ste /
NK015(ba)015:875: brten par bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK015(ba)015:876: dngos grub blang ba'i phyir dam la gzhugs pa dang /
NK015(ba)015:877: las kyi mkha' 'gro la dam tshig gi phyag rgya stod pa dang /
NK015(ba)015:884: bla ma shar ba spob pa mtha' yas kyis sbyar ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:885: khrag 'thung gi dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring gang yang rung ste /
NK015(ba)015:886: spyi don gsum gyis bstan pa ni /
NK015(ba)015:887: sngon du bya ba'i las dang mchod cing bsnyen pa'i las dang /
NK015(ba)015:888: mnag pa nan tur gyi las bya ba'o //
NK015(ba)015:889: mchod cing bsnyen pa'i las bya ba la /
NK015(ba)015:891: khro bo sngon gyi gleng gzhi brjod cing dal bstan pa dang /
NK015(ba)015:896: dam tshig gi phyag rgya bstan pa dang /
NK015(ba)015:899: phyag rgya gar tshogs kyi mchod pa bya ba dang /
NK015(ba)015:900: kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa dang /
NK015(ba)015:905: khams gsum yongs sgrol gyi mchod pa dang /
